        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="notice-box">
                <h2>Important Service Notice</h2>
                <p><strong>PantherMedia has ceased operations on panthermedia.net</strong></p>
                <p>After many years of serving the creative community, we have discontinued our services as of this date. We would like to express our sincere gratitude to all our customers, contributors, and partners who have been part of our journey.</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 1.3em; font-weight: bold;">Thank you for all these years of business.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <div class="copyright-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Copyright Infringement Notice from Copytrack?</h2>
                
                <div class="info-block">
                    <h3>If You Received a Notice from Copytrack GmbH or RD Legal GmbH</h3>
                    <p>If you have received a copyright infringement notice regarding PantherMedia images from <span class="highlight">Copytrack GmbH</span> or <span class="highlight">RD Legal GmbH</span>, please follow the instructions below to resolve your case.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-block">
                    <h3>How to Make a Payment</h3>
                    <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Locate your Case ID in the email or letter you received from Copytrack. It typically appears in the format: <span class="highlight">Case ID: XXXXXX</span></p>
                    
                    <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Visit the Copytrack payment portal:</p>
                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 15px 0;"><a href="https://portal.copytrack.com" target="_blank" style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: bold;">portal.copytrack.com</a></p>
                    
                    <p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Enter your Case ID when prompted</p>
                    
                    <p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Review the case details and payment options presented</p>
                    
                    <p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Complete payment through one of the following methods:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>PayPal</li>
                        <li>Credit Card</li>
                        <li>Bank Transfer</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="search-box">
                    <h3>Access Payment Portal</h3>
                    <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 20px;">Click the button below to access the Copytrack payment portal. You will need your Case ID to proceed with payment.</p>
                    <button class="search-button" onclick="window.open('https://portal.copytrack.com', '_blank')">Go to Copytrack Payment Portal</button>
                </div>

                <div class="payment-info">
                    <p><strong>Payment Options Explained:</strong></p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 15px;"><strong>Option 1 - Subsequent License:</strong> Purchase a license that covers past use and grants future use rights for one year</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 10px;"><strong>Option 2 - Compensation:</strong> Pay compensation for past use and immediately remove the image from your website</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 20px; color: #666;"><em>Note: Payment amounts are calculated based on the copyright holder's license history, duration of use, and type of infringement.</em></p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-block">
                    <h3>Need Assistance?</h3>
                    <p>For questions regarding your copyright infringement case, please contact:</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 15px;"><strong>Copytrack GmbH</strong><br>
                    Phone: <a href="tel:+493080933291">+49 30 809 332 910</a><br>
                    Available: Monday - Friday, 9:00 AM - 1:00 PM CET<br>
                    Email: <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#583b37362c393b2c183b3728212c2a393b33763b3735"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="01626e6f7560627541626e7178757360626a2f626e6c">[email&#160;protected]</span></a></p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-block">
                    <h3>If You Have Proof of License</h3>
                    <p>If you have documentation proving you purchased a valid license for the image in question:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Reply to the original email from Copytrack</li>
                        <li>Attach your proof of purchase or license agreement</li>
                        <li>Include any relevant transaction records</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p style="margin-top: 15px;">If your license is valid, Copytrack will close your case immediately.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2025 PantherMedia. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>For copyright enforcement inquiries, please contact Copytrack GmbH directly.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script data-cfasync="false" src="/cdn-cgi/scripts/5c5dd728/cloudflare-static/email-decode.min.js"></script><script>
        // No JavaScript needed for simple link button
    </script>
</body>
</html>
